      <li><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.10997" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gao et al. (2024), <em>Retrieval-Augmented Generation for Large Language Models: A Survey</em></a>: comprehensive overview of RAG techniques, architectures, and evaluation.</li>
